## Running Tests

```bash
# From the deepresearch workspace
cd workspaces/deepresearch

# Run all tests
pytest tests/ -v

# Run with coverage
pytest tests/ -v --cov=deepresearch

# Run a specific test file
pytest tests/test_orchestrator.py -v
```

